        "SS2_DIFFICULTY_TYPHOON_DESC": "Maximum challenge. The world is a nightmare, and survival is merely an illusion. Nobody has what it takes.<style=cStack>\n\n>Player Health Regeneration: <style=cIsHealth>-40%</style>\n>Difficulty Scaling: <style=cIsHealth>+75%</style>\n>Monster Spawn Limit: <style=cIsHealth>+100%</style>\n>Monster Spawn Rate: <style=cIsHealth>+25%</style>\n>Gold and Experience Rewards: <style=cisHealth>-20%</style>",
